22
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:34,540
The whole Japanese business community is desperately vying for his attention!

23
00:01:37,060 --> 00:01:38,320
Why is he laughing?

24
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:43,200
So, Mr. Yamamoto will not be able to meet with you today.

25
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:49,040
But I can say that I knew Kenzo Tenma just as well as he did, so feel free to ask anything.

26
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:50,520
But of course.

27
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:55,460
I have to say, Inspector, I'm shocked. He's still under investigation?

28
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:59,100
Well, I'll just say that we haven't come to any conclusions.

29
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:05,300
