30
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:08,460
You just said you felt shocked. Was it really that unexpected?

31
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:12,200
Absolutely. Kenzo Tenma, a killer?

32
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:24,040
Come on, it's just crazy. Not in a million years would I have pegged Tenma as a killer.

33
