Actually, Father, I'm a mother now.

55
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,160
I had my baby.

56
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:15,560
I thought you'd want to know.

57
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:18,720
I see. That's good.

58
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,820
I know a lot of things have been said between us.

59
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:25,440
But I want you to see your grandchild.

60
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,600
Will you see us?

61
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,860
Well, would tomorrow be okay?

62
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:34,820
Yes, as long as it's after six.

63
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,880
Where would you like to meet?

64
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,840
Near Mary in Platz?

65
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,500
Okay. All right.

66
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:43,300
See you then.

67
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:44,500
Domo.

68
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:45,660
What?

69
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:54,940
Hey, you're pretty good with those chopsticks, you know that?

70
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,440
Is that so?

71
