92
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:36,400
He seems to be a busy man.

93
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:41,420
If it's any consolation, he did say he was going to join all of us at a bar after work.

94
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,020
A bar?

95
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:45,200
That's right. Care to join us for a drink, Inspector?

96
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,780
The Fates have delivered you this opportunity.

97
00:07:49,780 --> 00:07:53,040
After all, it's always good to make a few new contacts.

98
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:01,700
No. Tonight I have to.

99
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:07,300
I guess he and his family weren't all that tight-knit, you know what I mean?

100
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:12,160
I am... Tenma.

101
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:19,180
Sounds great. I would be happy to join you tonight.

