Ah, domo, domo. I'm sorry I'm late, guys.

123
00:09:58,460 --> 00:10:00,560
Oh, there you are, Yamamoto.

124
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:05,580
Inspector Lunge, you know, the one I told you about on the phone.

125
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:09,200
Oh, domo. I'm Yamamoto of the Munich branch of the Katafuku.

126
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,680
Domo.

127
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:16,620
So, how did it go with Mr. Kocht in the Czech Republic?

128
